# Simplified <%= BasketContent.model_name.human %> Distribution

The <%= BasketContent.model_name.human.downcase %> distribution form no longer has separate "Automatic" and "Manual" tabs. Everything now lives in a single pane where you set per-size quantities directly, adjust the split with the same percentage sliders and presets from the old "Automatic" mode.

When a unit price is set, each adjustment automatically displays total prices and <%= Basket.model_name.human.downcase %> counts on the fly. No more saving and coming back to check whether the numbers are correct.

On top of that, the system now only saves the quantity for each size, so any last-minute change in the number of <%= Basket.model_name.human(count: 2).downcase %> is automatically taken into account. ✨

I have a few more improvement ideas in mind, but in the meantime don't hesitate to [let me know](/support) if you have suggestions or if these changes cause any issues.

Find more information in [the handbook](/handbook/basket_content#configuring-basket-contents).
